In [54]:
df = pd.read_csv('./data/overlap_address/profile.csv')[:]
df['date_uni'] = df.date_uni.astype('datetime64[ns]')
df['date_sushi'] = df.date_sushi.astype('datetime64[ns]')
df['transaction'] = df.transaction.astype('int32')
data = [(df.date_uni.values[i], df.date_sushi.values[i], df.transaction.values[i]) for i in range(0, len(df))]
scatter = hv.Scatter(data, vdims=['y', 'z'])
scatter.opts(
    title="First Interaction Date (Color-Total Transaction Count)",
    width=800,
    height=700,
    color='z',
    cmap='plasma',
    clim=(10, 2000),
    bgcolor='dimgray',
    colorbar=True,
    xrotation=45,
    xlabel='Uniswap',
    ylabel='Sushiswap',
    padding=(0, 0)
    )
scatter.hist(dimension=['x','y'])
# scatter + scatter[0.3:0.7, 0.3:0.7].hist()
